text:
@wwrdbruh @FynnInvests Funny, “incredibly late on the stock” was the argument at 50 - 80 SEK too.

So if $SIVE at a ~$2.5B market cap has already been re-rated, why are photonics peers like $LITE and $COHR trading at ~$70B+?

I don’t have anything against $IQE either. You’re just wrong is all.

